SELECT symbol FROM major WHERE name_arabic = '[major-name]';
SELECT i.office_hours FROM faculty f JOIN instructor i ON f.dean_id = i.id WHERE f.name_arabic = 'name_arabic' OR f.symbol = 'name_arabic';
